# Grimverse Thumbnail Rule

Thumbnail prompts should:
- keep one focal subject
- maximize face readability
- favor strong silhouette contrast
- avoid lore bloat
- prioritize click-through clarity

## Output
- Thumbnail prompt
- Optional title cue
- Optional composition cue
- Optional contrast cue

## Rule
If the thumbnail prompt is longer than the shot prompt, compress it.
